snippet.title: Breakout Beyond - Official Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Breakout Beyond is coming March 25, 2025! Power up and break through the bricks in this fast-paced, neon-drenched brick breaker. Breakout Beyond is coming soon!

Pre-Order Breakout Beyond: https://urals.co/atari/breakout-beyond
